Eisulie Saul Ilamoni


1  Neitoki Nahash, ilo Amoni, ailep alo neman Yabesh-gilead; nejoki iltung'ana pooki le Yabesh Nahash, “Ntaiki iyiook olning'o pee kisiaai iyie.” 
2  Kake etiaaka ninye Nahash, ilo Amori, “Tena oitoi aitaiki intae olning'o nchere kakurtu nanu nkonyek inyi pooki e tatene, napik esulare Israel pooki.” 
3  Nejoki ilpayiani le Yabesh ninye, “Nchoo iyiook muro too nkolong'i naapishana pee kitum aairriwai ilkiliku enkop pooki e Israel. Ore ake pee metii hoo obo oitajeu iyiook, nikincho iyiook iyie ate.” 
4  Ore ake pee epuonu ilkiliku Gibea e Saul, nelikioo ninche olomoni too nkiyiaa oo ltung'ana; neishir iltung'ana pooki aayietu.


5  Negira Saul alotu te nkurma te siadi ilmong'i; nejo Saul, “Kainyoo naishirie iltung'ana, pee eishirita?” Neliki ninche ilomon le lelo tung'ana le Yabesh. 
6  Nelotu enkiyang'et e Nkai te ngolon shumata Saul pee eidip atoning'o kulo omon, neyupuyup oleng engoro enye. 
7  Neya ninye ilmong'i oare ootii enchata emurt nabo, nedung'udung ninche aitaa ndung'ot, neirriwaa nena dung'ot enkop pooki e Israel, too nkaik e lelo kiliku ejo, “Ore pooki ng'ae lemeipang'u asuj Saul o Samuel, neikoni neijia ilmong'i lenyena!” Nejing iltung'ana euriata e Nkai, neipang'u ninche anaa oltung'ani obo. 
8  Ore ake pee eiturrur aiken ninche te Besek, nera iltung'ana le Israel nkalifuni iip uni, ore iltung'ana le Yuda naa nkalifuni tomoni uni. 
9  Nejoki ninche lelo ooetuo ooata olkilikuai, “Entiaaki iltung'ana le Yabesh-gilead inji, ‘Ore taisere, te neirouaju enkolong, nitumutumu intae enkordunoto.’ ” Ore pee epuonu lelo lo ilkilikuai neliki iltung'ana le Yabesh, neng'idayu ninche. 
10  Neaku etejo iltung'ana le Yabesh, “Ore taisere naa eikipalari iyiook te ntae, naa indimidimi aaitaasa iyiook enaba anaa enidolidolo aa sidai te ntae.” 
11  Ore pee ekenyu nepik Saul lelo tung'ana ilturrurri okuni; nepuonu ninche atua empolos oo lng'oborri tadekenya enasirie, nedung lelo Amoni o meipira enkolong; ore lelo ooimishote neidapasha, o metaba anaa neaku meetae ninye oare lenye ootoni te nebo.


12  Nejoki iltung'ana Samuel, “Kaing'ae ilo apa otejo, ‘Eji keitore iyiook Saul?’ Entoriku lelo tung'ana pee kiar iyiook metuata.” 
13  Kake etejo Saul, “Meari ninye oltung'ani obo metua ena olong, amu ore taata neyaua Olaitoriani enkordunoto ti atua Israel.” 
14  Neitoki Samuel ajoki iltung'ana, “Wootu, maapeiti iyiook Gilgal paa te ine kintang'ejuk enkitoria.” 
15  Neaku eshomo iltung'ana pooki Gilgal, ore te ine neitaa ninche Saul olaiguanani te dukuya Olaitoriani te Gilgal. Ore te ine nepolos ninche ilasarri le seriani te dukuya Olaitoriani; ore te ine neshipa Saul o ltung'ana pooki le Israel oleng.

